# Database Configuration
# ======================

# Development (SQLite)
DATABASE_URL="file:./dev.db"
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=""
ANTHROPIC_MODEL="claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929"

# Production (Supabase PostgreSQL)
# Replace with your Supabase connection strings:
# DATABASE_URL="postgresql://postgres:[PASSWORD]@db.[PROJECT-REF].supabase.co:5432/postgres?pgbouncer=true"
# DIRECT_URL="postgresql://postgres:[PASSWORD]@db.[PROJECT-REF].supabase.co:5432/postgres"

# Note: DATABASE_URL uses connection pooling (port 6543), DIRECT_URL uses direct connection (port 5432)
# The DIRECT_URL is used for migrations, while DATABASE_URL is used for queries


